abstract: >-
  Per-question evaluation records and the evaluation harness for the study
  "Embedded Agentic Retrieval (EAR): Answer-Quality Parity With Multi-Call
  Agentic RAG at a Single Generator Call." Includes six-pipeline results on four
  corpora, a cross-family judge run, a cross-family generation run, ablations,
  a combined-index multi-document experiment, and the reproducible harness.
